On your eye?

33
00:02:21,733 --> 00:02:23,067
Hey!

34
00:02:23,067 --> 00:02:25,933
Wow, Poo Gi Jeong's so manly.

35
00:02:25,933 --> 00:02:27,533
That sounds so romantic.

36
00:02:27,533 --> 00:02:28,600
Hey.

37
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,933
