63
00:03:29,433 --> 00:03:31,467
- Jo Mi Rae!
- Jo Mi Rae!

64
00:03:35,367 --> 00:03:40,333
Since he kissed her tears,
draw a heart right here.

65
00:03:41,233 --> 00:03:42,467
Jawline.

66
00:03:42,467 --> 00:03:45,867
