749
00:43:41,767 --> 00:43:44,767
Don't ever think about how charming I am.

750
00:43:44,767 --> 00:43:48,100
Don't ever miss me.

751
00:43:48,100 --> 00:43:51,900
Don't ever think of me in a new light.

752
